description:
After healing the daughter of Jairus by the sea of Galilee, Jesus now travels inland to his hometown, Nazareth. When you think of home, perhaps you think of a place of love and acceptance. Hes been looking to rest, and youd think that hed find it back home. But sadly, thats not what happens at all.
